name: Global Governance
description: This seminar course provides an orientation to the study of contemporary world order. Topics may include important legacies of the world wars of the 20th century, theories of conflict and cooperation, and new forms of transnational collaboration. Open only to students admitted to Trinity One. Not eligible for CR/NCR option.
exclusions: Innis One, Munk One, New One, St. Mike's One, Vic One, UC One, Woodsworth One
